dct_title_s: A Topographic Map of the Counties of Bergen, Hudson and Essex, with Parts of Passaic and Union
dct_description_sm: The historical map of New Jersey published originally by the Geological Survey of New Jersey was scanned, georeferenced and reprojected to the New Jersey State Plane Coordinate System, NAD 83 using ERDAS IMAGINE software.
